### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Agent365 registration metadata
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/agent365/registration

### Invoke - supported jurisdiction with risk check
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/agent/invoke
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "country": "Canada",
  "stateOrProvince": "Ontario",
  "cityOrMunicipality": "Toronto",
  "buildingType": "Mixed-use",
  "occupancyClass": "Residential and retail",
  "designStage": "Schematic",
  "query": "Check pre-permit risk for this concept",
  "designParameters": {
    "floors": "14",
    "heightMeters": "52"
  }
}

### Invoke - unsupported jurisdiction
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/agent/invoke
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "country": "Brazil",
  "buildingType": "Hospital",
  "occupancyClass": "Healthcare",
  "designStage": "Concept",
  "query": "What constraints apply?",
  "designParameters": {}
}

